### 1. Create a New User Profile (POST Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Mary Jane",
  "lastName": "O'Connor"
}

### 2. Fetch All User Profiles (GET Request)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### 3. Fetch Specific User Profile By ID (Replace 1 with your actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/1

### 4. Delete Specific Profile By ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/users/1
